Story time. Yesterday I played a fun game of Sheriff Commander (5-person) where I played Gonti as the deputy. The sheriff was playing Breya Eggs while the Renegade played Phanex mill. It was late game and the sheriff was ready to win so he played [[Open the Vaults]] to bring everything back and go off. I took one look at my gy, noticed my [[Leyline of the Void]] and almost shouted "Nooooo! " But it was too late. The sheriff looked at me in confusion until I pointed out the Leyline and he sank. Fortunately it gave me enough juice to Gary the remaining Outlaw to win the game for the sheriff but it was pretty funny.
